0Los%20Angeles-based%20FBI%20agent%20who%20specializes%20in%20investigating%20political%20corruption%20and%20foreign-influence%20campaigns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Johnson%2C%20a%20longtime%20associate%20of%20Thiel's%20and%20a%20notorious%20figure%20in%20the%20far-right%20movement%20that%20Thiel%20has%20subsidized%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20he%20helped%20recruit%20the%20billionaire%20as%20an%20informant%20by%20introducing%20him%20to%20Buma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20Thiel's%20relationship%20to%20the%20FBI%2C%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Insider%20but%20who%20insisted%20on%20anonymity%2C%20corroborated%20Johnson's%20account%2C%20telling%20Insider%20that%20Johnson%20brokered%20a%20relationship%20between%20Thiel%20and%20Buma.%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20confirm%20through%20an%20additional%20source%20that%20the%20FBI%20added%20Thiel%20to%20its%20formal%20roster%20of%20registered%20informants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20close%20to%20Thiel%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20they%20could%20not%20confirm%20that%20Thiel%20was%20a%20CHS%2C%20Thiel%20did%20speak%20to%20Buma%20occasionally.%20The%20source%20said%20that%20any%20assistance%20Thiel%20might%20have%20provided%20to%20the%20FBI%20should%20be%20understood%20as%20part%20of%20Thiel's%20gradual%20distancing%20of%20himself%20from%20Trump%20and%20the%20broader%20MAGA%20movement%2C%20which%20has%20vigorously%20criticized%20the%20FBI%20and%20other%20federal%20law-enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EValuable%20information%20on%20a%20recurring%20basis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20maintains%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20informants%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20organized%20crime%2C%20terrorist%20threats%2C%20extremist%20groups%2C%20and%20other%20criminal%20and%20intelligence%20targets.%20These%20sources%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bureau's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvault.fbi.gov%2Fconfidential-human-source-policy-guide-1018pg%2Fconfidential-human-source-policy-guide-1018pg-part-01-of-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConfidential%20Human%20Source%20Policy%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20more%20than%20casual%20tipsters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConfidential%20human%20sources%20enter%20%26quot%3Binto%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20FBI%2C%20and%20that%20relationship%20will%20forever%20affect%20the%20life%20of%20that%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guide%20says.%20%26quot%3B%5BThey%5D%20will%20be%20either%20an%20'FBI%20source'%20or%20a%20'former%20FBI%20source'%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20his%20or%20her%20conduct%20or%20misconduct%20will%20reflect%20upon%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%20As%20such%2C%20the%20process%20for%20recruiting%20and%20maintaining%20such%20sources%20is%20highly%20regulated%2C%20requiring%20multiple%20layers%20of%20approval.%20Only%20people%20who%20are%20able%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%20information%20%E2%80%A6%20on%20a%20recurring%20basis%26quot%3B%20are%20granted%20CHS%20status%2C%20according%20to%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Pence%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Peter%20Thiel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65307fa5be9edfa8eda45cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22618%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThen%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Peter%20Thiel%20during%20a%20meeting%20at%20Trump%20Tower%20in%20December%202016.%20Years%20later%2C%20Thiel%20would%20become%20a%20confidential%20human%20source%20for%20the%20FBI.%20He%20was%20directed%20not%20to%20report%20on%20his%20interactions%20with%20Trump%20or%20other%20US%20political%20figures%2C%20an%20associate%20said.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20CHS%2C%20Thiel%20was%20assigned%20a%20code%20name%20and%20an%20internal%20serial%20number%20to%20track%20his%20reporting.%20The%20information%20he%20passed%20on%20about%20foreign%20contacts%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%20intrigue%20was%20reviewed%20and%20%26quot%3Bvalidated%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20cross-checked%20against%20other%20sources%2C%20by%20his%20case%20agents%20and%20their%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.%20A%20Thiel%20spokesperson%20stopped%20responding%20to%20inquiries%20after%20being%20told%20that%20Insider%20was%20reporting%20on%20Thiel's%20relationship%20with%20the%20FBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI's%20national%20press%20office%20and%20Scott%20Horton%2C%20an%20attorney%20who%20represents%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20both%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20reporting%20on%20political%20ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20is%20a%20citizen%20of%20Germany%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%3B%20as%20of%20last%20year%2C%C2%A0%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F10%2F15%2Ftechnology%2Fpeter-thiel-malta-citizenship.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20in%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20acquiring%20yet%20another%20passport%2C%20from%20Malta.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20donated%20%241.25%20million%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20and%20endorsed%20him%20from%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention.%20After%20Trump%20won%2C%20Thiel%20served%20on%20his%20transition%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20said%20that%20he%20was%20also%20an%20informant%20for%20Buma%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20Thiel's%20reporting%20to%20the%20FBI%20was%20largely%20limited%20to%20foreign%20contacts%20and%20attempts%20by%20foreign%20governments%20to%20penetrate%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Thiel%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2Fpeter-thiel-reportedly-says-the-fbi-and-cia-should-investigate-google.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicly%20called%20on%20the%20FBI%20to%20investigate%20Google's%20ties%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%2C%20Johnson%20said%2C%20was%20directed%20by%20the%20FBI%20not%20to%20report%20on%20his%20interactions%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20or%20other%20US%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20politicians%20that%20Thiel%20has%20bankrolled%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Trump%2C%20Sen.%20J.D.%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%2C%20and%20Blake%20Masters%2C%20a%20former%20Arizona%20senatorial%20candidate%20%E2%80%94%20have%20repeatedly%20attacked%20the%20bureau%20and%20its%20leadership%20in%20public.%20In%202022%2C%20Vance%2C%20whose%20campaign%20and%20affiliated%20PACs%20received%20a%20total%20of%20%2415%20million%20from%20Thiel%2C%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20the%20FBI%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-falsely-claims-fbi-illegally-wiretapped-trump-ohio-rally-2022-4%5C%22%3Eillegally%20wiretapped%20Trump's%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Vance%20accused%20the%20bureau%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJDVance1%2Fstatus%2F1624079332711825409%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharassing%20faithful%20Christians%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20pledged%20to%20block%20all%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Department%20of%20Justice%20nominees%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20Trump%20prosecutions.%20(Most%20but%20not%20all%20of%20Thiel's%20donations%20occurred%20in%20early%202021%2C%20before%20the%20launch%20of%20Vance's%20campaign%20and%20the%20many%20false%20claims%20he%20made%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20race.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653082e6211def8ed838ce71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20serving%20as%20an%20FBI%20informant%2C%20Thiel%20bankrolled%20the%20campaign%20of%20now-Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%20of%20Ohio.%20Vance%20has%20made%20a%20number%20of%20false%20and%20disparaging%20claims%20about%20the%20FBI.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMasters%2C%20whose%20campaign%20received%20%2420%20million%20of%20support%20from%20Thiel%2C%20has%20endorsed%20the%20false%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20undercover%20FBI%20agents%20fomented%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20insurrection%20and%20accused%20the%20FBI%20agents%20who%20executed%20a%20search%20warrant%20on%20Mar-a-Lago%20of%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20after%20President%20Trump%20because%20they%20hate%20him.%26quot%3B%20(As%20with%20Vance%2C%20most%20but%20not%20all%20of%20Thiel's%20donations%20to%20Masters%20occurred%20before%20Masters%20made%20his%20most%20inflammatory%20and%20baseless%20statements%20during%20the%20later%20stages%20of%20his%20campaign.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20is%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpeter-thiel-republican-megadonor-wont-fund-candidates-2024-sources-2023-04-26%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20reportedly%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Trump%2C%20Masters%2C%20nor%20Vance%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoing%20business%20with%20the%20FBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Thiel's%20business%20interests%20rely%20on%20the%20FBI%20and%20other%20government%20agencies%20as%20potential%20revenue%20sources.%20He%20retains%20a%2010%25%20stake%20in%20Palantir%2C%20a%20data%20company%20that%20has%20sold%20more%20than%20a%20billion%20dollars%20of%20software%20and%20related%20services%20to%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20including%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20the%20CIA%2C%20the%20National%20Security%20Agency%2C%20and%20the%20FBI.%20A%20%24250%20million%20contract%20with%20the%20US%20Army%20in%20September%20adds%20to%20the%20evidence%20that%20Palantir%20is%20essentially%20%26quot%3Ba%20government%20service%20provider%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20financial%20analyst%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investors.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fpltr-stock-palantir-wins-250-million-army-ai-services-contract%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fthomasbrewster%2F2022%2F02%2F01%2Fbillionaire-facebook-investor-peter-thiel-secretly-funded-a-cyber-warfare-startup-that-hacked-whatsapp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dreddit%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dforbes%26sh%3D7e49fa2d5600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20also%20backed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Boldend%2C%20a%20spyware%20company%20marketing%20itself%20as%20an%20American%20competitor%20to%20the%20Israeli%20NSO%20Group%2C%20Forbes%20reported%20last%20year.%20NSO's%20products%20have%20been%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F01%2F28%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-pegasus-spyware.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20bought%20and%20tested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20FBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Mithril%20Capital%2C%20another%20entity%20Thiel%20cofounded%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-mithril-capital-fbi-investigation-venture-capital-financial-misconduct-2019-9%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20a%20subject%20of%20FBI%20interest%20in%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20nothing%20appears%20to%20have%20come%20of%20the%20inquiry.%20Mithril's%20co-founder%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20The%20FBI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20question%20regarding%20the%20Mithril%20matter.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20revealed%20Thiel's%20FBI%20ties%2C%20is%20a%20tech%20investor%20and%20far-right%20agitator%20with%20long-standing%20ties%20to%20both%20Thiel%20and%20to%20the%20network%20of%20MAGA%20political%20operators%20surrounding%20Trump.%20He%20claims%20to%20have%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20founding%20Clearview%2C%20a%20facial-recognition%20startup%2C%20and%20Traitwell%2C%20a%20genomics%20company.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fmattdrange%2F2017%2F01%2F09%2Fchuck-johnson-troll-trump-transition-team%2F%3Fsh%3D5474e3a0265e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Forbes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20Thiel%20to%20help%20vet%20and%20select%20senior%20staffers%20for%20the%20Trump%20transition%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20FBI%20informant%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdockets.justia.com%2Fdocket%2Fnew-york%2Fnysdce%2F1%3A2023cv02441%2F596057%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20filed%20against%20Clearview's%20founders.%20He%20told%20Insider%20he%20recruited%20Thiel%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20CHS%20and%20introduced%20him%20to%20Buma%2C%20the%20FBI%20special%20agent%20who%20was%20Johnson's%20handler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charles%20Johnson%20with%20Matt%20Gaetz%20and%20Ginger%20Gaetz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65308922be9edfa8eda45e39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharles%20Johnson%20(left)%20with%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz%20(right)%20and%20Gaetz's%20now-wife%20Ginger%20Gaetz%20(center)%2C%20in%202021.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20brokered%20an%20introduction%20between%20Thiel%20and%20the%20FBI%20special%20agent%20who%20would%20become%20his%20handler.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20Thiel%20remains%20a%20CHS%20for%20the%20FBI.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20the%20relationship%20has%20been%20severed%20but%20declined%20to%20offer%20details%3B%20Buma%20wrote%20in%20his%20statement%20to%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%20that%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20cease%20contact%20with%20all%20his%20sources%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20ties%20to%20Trump%20and%20Thiel%20are%20well-documented.%20But%20he%20is%20also%20a%20self-identified%20%26quot%3Btroll%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20history%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%20and%20smearing%20his%20rivals.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20his%20claims%20are%20corroborated%20by%20two%20additional%20sources%2C%20as%20well%20as%20supported%20in%20part%20by%20a%20third%20who%20says%20Thiel%20and%20Buma%20spoke%20occasionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Join%20up%20or%20get%20crushed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuma%20came%20forward%20in%20August%20as%20a%20whistleblower%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20FBI%20under%20Trump%20and%20Attorney%20General%20Bill%20Barr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-didnt-care-giuliani-compromised-by-kremlin-whistleblower-buma-2023-9%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%20his%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20determine%20whether%20Rudy%20Giuliani%20had%20been%20compromised%20by%20a%20Russian%20asset.%20Insider%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-whistleblower-senate-judiciary-russia-giuliani-leak-trump-allies-fuks-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20news%20organization%20to%20report%20on%20his%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20prepared%20for%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%2C%20Buma%20said%20that%20FBI%20headquarters%20had%20closed%20his%20most%20valuable%20human%20sources%2C%20including%20one%20code-named%20%26quot%3BGenius%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20reported%20on%20far-right%20figures%20involved%20with%20planning%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%2C%202021.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3BGenius%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20CHS%20code%20name.%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20confirm%20Johnson's%20identity%20as%20%26quot%3BGenius%26quot%3B%20with%20two%20additional%20sources.%20The%C2%A0statement%20does%20not%20mention%20Thiel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Thiel%20at%20the%20RNC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653086d6211def8ed838cf20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThiel%20speaking%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%202016.%20He%20donated%20%241.25%20million%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20in%202016.%20He%20backed%20MAGA-aligned%20congressional%20candidates%20in%202020%20and%202022.%20He%20has%20said%20he%20will%20be%20staying%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%202024%20presidential%20race.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20was%20stepping%20forward%20as%20a%20CHS%20to%20support%20Buma's%20effort%20as%20a%20whistleblower%20to%20bring%20about%20what%20Buma%20believes%20to%20be%20necessary%20reforms%20in%20how%20the%20FBI%20handles%20informants.%20Johnson%20said%20that%20he%20was%20exposing%20Thiel's%20work%20as%20a%20CHS%20as%20retribution%20for%20what%20Johnson%20perceives%20to%20be%20bad%20decision-making%20by%20the%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20Thiel's%20venture-capital%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20also%20told%20Insider%20he%20felt%20betrayed%20that%20Thiel%20did%20not%20invest%20in%20Johnson's%20own%20startups%2C%20which%20he%20had%20expected%20Thiel%20to%20do%20in%20exchange%20for%20introducing%20him%20to%20Buma.%20Johnson%20said%20that%20he%20told%20Thiel%20that%20by%20offering%20the%20FBI%20a%20window%20into%20his%20contacts%20with%20foreign%20governments%2C%20he%20could%20demonstrate%20his%20loyalty%20to%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20Thiel's%20motivation%20for%20working%20with%20Buma%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20hedge%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20extravagant%20wealth%20no%20longer%20affords%2