20of%20marine%20mammal%20pens%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Black%20Sea%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20the%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceHQ%2Fstatus%2F1672118745991397376%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20in%20an%20intelligence%20update%20in%20June.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dolphins%20can%20detect%20any%20intruder%2C%20collect%20intelligence%2C%20or%20possibly%20even%20deliver%20a%20lethal%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-moves-trained-dolphins-closer-to-front-lines-ukraine-report-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711873000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530f24abe9edfa8eda475ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-moves-trained-dolphins-closer-to-front-lines-ukraine-report-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20moved%20its%20trained%20dolphins%20much%20closer%20to%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%20to%20help%20protect%20its%20naval%20forces%20from%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-moves-trained-dolphins-closer-to-front-lines-ukraine-report-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'blue%20dollar'%20is%20booming%3A%20Argentina's%20lust%20for%20the%20buck%20pushed%20its%20black-market%20rate%20up%2060%2C000%25%20since%20peso%20parity%20ended%20in%202002%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223993%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Argentina%20peso%2Fdollar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3bba3cf07780019663245%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222994%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20dollar%20and%20Argentine%20peso%20notes.%3Cp%3ENora%20Mazzini%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20Argentina's%20black%20market%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20recently%20climbed%20past%201%2C000%20pesos%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20price%20of%20%26quot%3Bblue%20dollars%26quot%3B%20surged%20almost%2060%2C000%25%20since%20Argentina%20scrapped%20its%20currency%20peg%20in%202002.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20greenback%20allows%20Argentines%20to%20protect%20their%20earnings%20as%20the%20peso%20keeps%20losing%20its%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Argentina's%20economy%20and%20markets%2C%20chaos%20is%20a%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20nation%20has%20been%20roiled%20by%20hyperinflation%2C%20sky-high%20interest%20rates%2C%20a%20growing%20mountain%20of%20debt%2C%20a%20string%20of%20sovereign%20defaults%2C%20and%20a%20cratering%20exchange%20rate.%20It's%20been%20in%20recession%20for%20a%20third%20of%20the%20time%20since%201950%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsantandertrade.com%2Fen%2Fportal%2Fanalyse-markets%2Fargentina%2Feconomic-political-outline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Spain's%20Santander%20Group%20that%20cited%20World%20Bank%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20week%2C%20the%20country's%20central%20bank%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftradingeconomics.com%2Fargentina%2Finterest-rate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejacked%20up%20its%20benchmark%20interest%20rate%20to%20a%20stunning%20133%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20(yes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right)%2C%20stepping%20up%20a%20seemingly%20losing%20battle%20against%20consumer-price%20increases%20that%20came%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftradingeconomics.com%2Fargentina%2Finflation-cpi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20140%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERampant%20inflation%20has%20ravaged%20Argentina's%20currency%20over%20the%20years%2C%20wiping%20out%20much%20of%20its%20value%20against%20the%20dollar%20and%20ruining%20its%20appeal%20to%20consumers.%20The%20greenback%20has%20surged%20almost%20100%25%20this%20year%20to%20about%20350%20pesos%20in%20the%20interbank%20market%2C%20with%20even%20triple-digit%20interest%20rates%20failing%20to%20prop%20up%20the%20local%20tender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERise%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bblue%20dollar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20just%20the%20official%20side%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Argentina's%20bustling%20black%20market%20for%20foreign%20currencies%2C%20the%20dollar%20is%20far%20dearer.%20US%20currency%20bills%20are%20much%20sought%20after%20by%20residents%20as%20a%20means%20to%20protect%20their%20savings%2C%20which%20risk%20losing%20value%20by%20the%20day%20if%20held%20in%20the%20hapless%20local%20currency.%20Argentines%20have%20stashed%20away%20billions%20of%20cash%20dollars%20in%20their%20cupboards%20and%20under%20mattresses%2C%20according%20to%20some%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coveted%20bucks%20from%20the%20back%20alleys%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%20have%20their%20own%20price%2C%20even%20their%20own%20name%3A%20d%C3%B3lar%20blue%2C%20or%20the%20%26quot%3Bblue%20dollar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20are%20always%20in%20demand%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUp%2060%2C000%25%20and%20going%20strong%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dollar's%20unofficial%20exchange%20rate%20smashed%20above%201%2C000%20pesos%20for%20the%20first%20time%20last%20week%2C%20to%20hit%20levels%20almost%20three%20times%20as%20high%20as%20the%20official%20rate.%20That's%20a%20gain%20of%20almost%20200%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20isn't%20just%20a%202023%20story.%20It's%20a%20theme%20that%20goes%20back%20just%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20when%20Argentina%20abandoned%20its%20exchange-rate%20peg%20versus%20the%20dollar%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20sharp%20devaluation%20of%20the%20peso.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20that%20seismic%20market%20event%2C%20dollar%20rates%20in%20Argentina's%20black%20market%20have%20skyrocketed%20almost%2060%2C000%25%2C%20according%20to%20Insider%20calculations%20based%20figures%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbluedollar.net%2Finformal-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebluedollar.net%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20data%20on%20the%20country's%20informal%20exchange%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20level%20of%20about%201.7%20pesos%20at%20the%20start%20of%202002%2C%20the%20figure%20was%201%2C010%20pesos%20last%20week%20%E2%80%93%20with%20some%20reports%20putting%20the%20blue%20dollar's%20peak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fargentina-peso-exchange-rate-dollarization-javier-milei-bullrich-inflation-interest-2023-10%5C%22%3Eas%20high%20as%201%2C050%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHidden%20dollar%20hoards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArgentines%20had%20hoarded%20about%20%24246%20billion%20in%20undeclared%20cash%2C%20overseas%20bank%20accounts%2C%20and%20safe-deposit%20boxes%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20the%20American%20libertarian%20think%20tank%20Cato%20Institute%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato.org%2Fblog%2Feconomist-gets-it-wrong-dollarization-argentina%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAt%2520the%2520end%2520of%25202022%2Cfor%25202021%2520(%2524487%2520billion)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20citing%20figures%20from%20Argentina's%20statistics%20agency.%20Local%20media%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuenosairesherald.com%2Feconomics%2Fdollar-peso%2Fall-argentinas-dollar-exchange-rates-explained%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBecause%2520of%2520that%252C%2520Argentines%2520prefer%2520to%2520store%2520their%2520crisp%2520banknotes%2520at%