0Tesla%20aiming%20to%20produce%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20million%20trucks%20a%20year%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20dug%20our%20own%20grave%20with%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20those%20special%20products%20that%20comes%20along%20only%20once%20in%20a%20long%20while.%20And%20special%20products%20that%20come%20along%20once%20in%20a%20long%20while%20are%20just%20incredibly%20difficult%20to%20bring%20to%20market%20to%20reach%20volume%2C%20to%20be%20prosperous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Btemper%20expectations%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-release-date-november-delivery-event-giga-texas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20truck's%20launch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Tesla%20announced%20would%20be%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20warned%20that%20the%20challenges%20of%20scaling%20up%20production%20meant%20that%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20around%2018%20months%20before%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20cash%20flow%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20want%20to%20emphasize%20that%20there%20will%20be%20enormous%20challenges%20in%20reaching%20volume%20production%20with%20the%20Cybertruck%20and%20then%20making%20the%20Cybertruck%20cashflow%20positive%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20simply%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you've%20got%20a%20product%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20technology%20or%20any%20brand%20new%20vehicle%20program%2C%20especially%20one%20that%20is%20as%20different%20and%20advanced%20as%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20you%20will%20have%20problems%20proportionate%20to%20how%20many%20new%20things%20you're%20trying%20to%20solve%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20the%20Cybertruck%20comes%20at%20a%20crucial%20time%20for%20Tesla.%20Although%20the%20company%20dominates%20the%2