%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20volunteer%20for%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20about%20the%20initiative%20through%20Instagram%20and%20was%20very%20intrigued.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20such%20an%20amazing%20movement.%20I%20have%20been%20volunteering%20with%20them%20from%20Raipur%20for%20the%20past%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharing%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20incidents%20as%20a%20listener%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20old%20woman%20who%20saw%20my%20sign%20and%20walked%20up%20to%20me.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20have%20so%20many%20stories%2C%20you%20will%20need%20all%20day%E2%80%99.%20I%20readily%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Come%2C%20let%20us%20sit%E2%80%99.%20She%20spoke%20to%20me%20for%2048%20minutes%20and%20told%20me%20how%20lonely%20she%20feels%20at%20home%2C%20now%20that%20her%20kids%20are%20all%20settled%20far%20away.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20talking%20to%20me%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20talking%20to%20her%20son.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20my%20day!%20Isolation%20among%20seniors%20is%20a%20topic%20that%20is%20rarely%20discussed.%20They%20mostly%20suffer%20alone%20and%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20I%20could%20be%20her%20friend%20that%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Raj%20has%20lost%20count%20of%20the%20number%20of%20stories%20he%E2%80%99s%20heard.%20%E2%80%9COne%20common%20thread%20runs%20through%20all%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20isolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tell%20them%20that%20even%20I%20once%20believed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20feeling%20depressed.%20But%20with%20the%20right%20support%20system%2C%20you%20can%20overcome%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzYGh6oYCS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_camp