20was%20the%20turning%20point%20in%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eempire%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khichdi%20express%20sells%20over%2030%20varieties%20of%20the%20dish%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKhicdhii-min-1697467926-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhichdi%20express%20sells%20over%2030%20varieties%20of%20the%20dish%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooling%20in%20all%20her%20life%20savings%20amounting%20to%20Rs%203%20lakhs%2C%20Abha%20and%20Mahendra%20started%20Khichdi%20Express%20in%20July%202019%20in%20Hyderabad%20as%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20with%20just%20one%20staff%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Mahendra%20suggested%20this%20business%2C%20I%20started%20doing%20some%20research%20and%20saw%20the%20popularity%20of%20this%20dish.%20I%20designed%20a%20menu%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20open%20the%20first%20branch%20in%20Hyderabad%20as%20rental%20spaces%20here%20are%20lower%20than%20those%20in%20Mumbai.%20It%20was%20just%20us%20and%20our%20kitchen%20member.%20We%20had%20nothing%20but%20our%20dreams%20when%20we%20first%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20sell%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330545%2Fakshay-ridlan-qr-code-locket-finding-lost-missing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20types%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Starting%20with%20the%20crowd%20favourites%20like%20dal%2C%20%3Cem%3Epalak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spinach)%20and%20mixed%20vegetable%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20menu%20moves%20on%20to%20fancier%20varieties%20like%20cheese%20chilly%2C%20%3Cem%3Epalak%20paneer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20pav%20bhaji%2C%20kolhapuri%2C%20corn%20mushroom%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20more.%20Their%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdis%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20209-349%20and%20are%20served%20with%20a%20papad%2C%20work%20as%20a%20whole%20meal%2C%20adds%20Abha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20first%20month%20of%20business%2C%20they%20earned%20enough%20to%20pay%20their%20staff%20members%20their%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20moments%20in%20her%20life%2C%20says%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20someone%20a%20salary%2C%20which%20was%20the%20same%20amount%20which%20I%20got%20in%20my%20first%20job%2C%20I%20felt%20so%20happy.%20What%20added%20to%20the%20happiness%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20from%20the%20profits%20and%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20take%20any%20loan%20or%20investment%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20sales%2C%20they%20opened%20their%20second%20branch%20in%20Mumbai%20within%20six%20months.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20eight%20branches%20across%20Mumbai%20