20has%20worked%20as%20a%20chef%20in%20numerous%20restaurants%20worldwide%20including%20Mexico%20and%20California%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20drawn%20to%20cooking%20naturally.%20A%20kitchen%20always%20brings%20family%20and%20friends%20together%3B%20an%20interesting%20space%20to%20be%20around.%20A%20kitchen%20is%20a%20place%20that%20can%20build%20perspectives%20on%20food%20and%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20around%20food%20has%20always%20prompted%20me%20to%20think%20of%20what%20happens%20to%20food%20before%20and%20after%20it%20is%20served%20on%20the%20plate.%20That%20curiosity%20and%20learning%20have%20shaped%20what%20my%20worth%20is%20as%20a%20cook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20her%20fondness%20for%20cooking%20took%20her%20to%20California%20where%20she%20worked%20with%20food%20historian%20William%20Rubel%2C%20who%20has%20been%20recreating%20breads%20from%20the%2017th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20one-month-long%20internship%2C%20she%20studied%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F212039%2Fparsi-cuisine-batasa-recipe-niloufer-book-food-history-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%20of%20bread%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20discovered%20the%20age-old%20relationship%20between%20a%20brewer%20and%20a%20baker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSpent-grains-1697464201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elizabeth%20says%20that%20she%20was%20able%20to%20upcycle%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20spent%20grain%20last%20financial%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSpent-grains-1697464201.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi