ious%20to%20incorporate%20the%20learnings%20into%20present-day%20work%2C%20she%20experimented%20with%20spent%20grain%20and%20upcycled%20it%20into%20products%20like%20flours%2C%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20granola%2C%20and%20even%20%3Cem%3Eladdus%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESpent%20grain%20into%20earthy%20loaves%2C%20laddus%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Elizabeth%20launched%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Saving%20Grains%E2%80%99%20to%20upcycle%20spent%20grains%20from%20breweries.%20These%20breweries%20use%20grains%20like%20barley%20and%20wheat%20in%20the%20process%20of%20brewing%20beers.%20The%20malted%20grains%20are%20soaked%20in%20hot%20water%20and%20then%20mashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCeaMiKph9TD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCeaMiKph9TD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCeaMiKph9TD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%