%20because%20she%20was%20a%20woman.%20Wanting%20to%20explore%20her%20talents%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20brother%20in%20idol-making%20when%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324344%2Fportia-putatunda-planet-spiti-foundation-boarding-school-for-underprivileged-kids-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20by%20sheer%20chance%20that%20I%20got%20to%20complete%20an%20idol%20and%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20client%20one%20day.%20My%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20to%20work%20on%20it%2C%20got%20caught%20up%20elsewhere%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%20With%20a%20deadline%20looming%20large%2C%20I%20took%20on%20the%20work%20as%20a%20challenge%20and%20completed%20it.%20Everyone%20was%20happy%20with%20the%20outcome%20and%20that%20was%20when%20I%20started%20getting%20noticed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297296%2Faward-winning-kumartuli-artisan-mala-pal-trains-youths-in-idol-making-for-kolkata-durga-puja%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamed%20potter%E2%80%99s%20quarter%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kumartuli%2C%20the%20business%20of%20making%20idols%20has%20long%20been%20male-dominated.%20The%20locality%20is%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20magic%20and%20frenzy%20of%20Durga%20%3Cem%3EPuja%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20biggest%20festival%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20small%20lanes%20of%20Kumartuli%20where%20hundreds%20of%20idols%20are%20made%20and%20shipped%20to%20the%20city%20and%20suburbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyZ50GoLy3v%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22ht