seven%20openings%20for%20JRF%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%20Applicants%20must%20not%20be%20more%20than%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20appointment%20of%20applicants%20is%20for%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years%20and%20may%20be%20extendable%20as%20per%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20For%20the%20position%20of%20JRF%2C%20candidates%20must%20have%20a%20BE%2C%20BTech%20in%20electronics%2F%20electronics%20and%20communication%2F%20applied%20electronics%2F%20signal%20processing%2F%20microwave%2F%20microelectronics%2F%20microwave%20engineering%2F%20power%20electronics%2F%20electronics%20and%20instrumentation%2F%20instrumentation%20and%20controls%20and%20similar%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Candidates%20should%20have%20secured%20a%20first%20division%20with%20NET%2FGATE%20qualification.%20Alternatively%2C%20candidates%20can%20have%20an%20MSc%2C%20ME%20or%20MTech%20in%20the%20above-mentioned%20disciplines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20Candidates%20can%20also%20possess%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20or%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20different%20disciplines%2C%20such%20as%20aeronautical%20engineering%20and%20computer%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E5.%20For%20the%20post%20of%20RA%2C%20the%20candidates%20must%20have%20done%20PhD%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296881%2Fengineering-student-converts-hyundai-santro-petrol-car-into-electric-vehicle-saves-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectronics%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E)%20or%20ME%2F%20MTech%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20years%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20experience%20in%20a%20reputed%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6.%20Candidates%20who%20have%20submitted%20their%20PhD%20theses%20may%20also%20apply%20for%20the%20post%20of%20RA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20note%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E1.%